request.description:
List of accounts with details.


Sample request:

    {
        "header": {
            "ID": "(uuid)",
            "application": "{{client_id}}"
        },
        "payload": {
            "ownAccounts": true,
            "userId": "123456"
        }
    }

NBG Account beneficiaries masked.

Sample request:

    {
        "header": {
            "ID": "(uuid)",
            "application": "{{client_id}}"
        },
        "payload": {
            "iban": "GR1601100400000004012345678",
            "userId": "123456"
        }
    }

Info about the logged in user (i.e. userId).

Sample request:

    {
        "header": {
            "ID": "(uuid)",
            "application": "{{client_id}}"
        },
        "payload": {
            "userId": "123456"
        }
    }
